          </a>          
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>
          National Crisis Line - Anorexia and Bulimia
          </strong>
          <br>
          <a href="tel:1-800-233-4357">
            1-800-233-4357
          </a>          
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>
          LGBT Hotline
          </strong> 
          <br>
          <a href="tel:18888434564">
            1-888-843-4564
          </a>          
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>
          TREVOR Crisis Hotline
          </strong> 
          <br>
          <a href="tel:18664887386">
            1-866-488-7386
          </a>
          
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>
          AIDS Crisis Line
          </strong> 
          <br>
          <a href="tel:18002217044">
            1-800-221-7044
